          "value": {
            "type": "blockComment",
            "value": "A gingerbread man cookie cutter is a charming kitchen tool designed in the iconic silhouette of a little person. Typically crafted from metal (often tin or stainless steel) or durable plastic, this cookie cutter features the distinctive outline of a stylized human figure with a round head, a simple torso, and extended arms and legs. The cutter's edges are sharp enough to cleanly slice through cookie dough but blunt enough to be handled safely.",
